      "start_time": 222.35,
      "recording_attendee_id": "8ceb7f8c-82e6-4fe3-9727-6265f68974f1",
      "order_number": 9,
      "text": "Hi there is this Amanda?"
    },
    {
      "id": "c693635b-fb64-48a0-9b4a-83d16f16e374",
      "recording_id": "37b4b58b-4a49-4350-a78b-68763881d8eb",
      "end_time": 224.74,
      "start_time": 224.02,
      "recording_attendee_id": "4c6e57ef-ad6a-417e-958b-067695f488b2",
      "order_number": 10,
      "text": "it is."
    },
    {
      "id": "c693635b-fb64-48a0-9b4a-83d16f16e374",
      "recording_id": "37b4b58b-4a49-4350-a78b-68763881d8eb",
      "end_time": 229.24,
      "start_time": 224.96,
      "recording_attendee_id": "8ceb7f8c-82e6-4fe3-9727-6265f68974f1",
      "order_number": 11,
      "text": "Hey Amanda. Good afternoon. It's Brandon common with rentable. How are you doing?"
    },
    {
      "id": "c693635b-fb64-48a0-9b4a-83d16f16e374",
      "recording_id": "37b4b58b-4a49-4350-a78b-68763881d8eb",
      "end_time": 232.19,
      "start_time": 230.9,
      "recording_attendee_id": "4c6e57ef-ad6a-417e-958b-067695f488b2",
      "order_number": 12,
      "text": "I'm fine. How are you?"
    },
    {
      "id": "c693635b-fb64-48a0-9b4a-83d16f16e374",
      "recording_id": "37b4b58b-4a49-4350-a78b-68763881d8eb",
      "end_time": 257.65,
      "start_time": 232.3,
      "recording_attendee_id": "8ceb7f8c-82e6-4fe3-9727-6265f68974f1",
      "order_number": 13,
      "text": "Good, good. Say the reason for my call um I was actually out on vacation last week, but my um my colleague Cameron had said that he had had a meeting set up and something came up and he had asked me to to try and get you back on the calendar for a quick ten to fifteen minute conversation was hoping uh was hoping we could reschedule that if you had some time uh maybe tomorrow or Wednesday?"
    },
    {
      "id": "c693635b-fb64-48a0-9b4a-83d16f16e374",
      "recording_id": "37b4b58b-4a49-4350-a78b-68763881d8eb",
      "end_time": 264.02,
      "start_time": 260.01,
      "recording_attendee_id": "4c6e57ef-ad6a-417e-958b-067695f488b2",
      "order_number": 14,
      "text": "Um Oh tomorrow won't work. You can try for Wednesday."
    },
    {
      "id": "c693635b-fb64-48a0-9b4a-83d16f16e374",
      "recording_id": "37b4b58b-4a49-4350-a78b-68763881d8eb",
      "end_time": 267.79,
      "start_time": 264.34,
      "recording_attendee_id": "8ceb7f8c-82e6-4fe3-9727-6265f68974f1",
      "order_number": 15,
      "text": "Okay, what time what time on Wednesday would would work best for you?"
    },
    {
      "id": "c693635b-fb64-48a0-9b4a-83d16f16e374",
      "recording_id": "37b4b58b-4a49-4350-a78b-68763881d8eb",
      "end_time": 271.27,
      "start_time": 270.1,
      "recording_attendee_id": "4c6e57ef-ad6a-417e-958b-067695f488b2",
      "order_number": 16,
      "text": "Let me ask you a question."
    },
    {
      "id": "c693635b-fb64-48a0-9b4a-83d16f16e374",
      "recording_id": "37b4b58b-4a49-4350-a78b-68763881d8eb",
      "end_time": 271.95,
      "start_time": 271.55,
      "recording_attendee_id": "8ceb7f8c-82e6-4fe3-9727-6265f68974f1",
      "order_number": 17,
      "text": "Yes."
    },
    {
      "id": "c693635b-fb64-48a0-9b4a-83d16f16e374",
      "recording_id": "37b4b58b-4a49-4350-a78b-68763881d8eb",
      "end_time": 275.4,
      "start_time": 273.92,
      "recording_attendee_id": "4c6e57ef-ad6a-417e-958b-067695f488b2",
      "order_number": 18,
      "text": "What were we talking about?"
    },
    {
      "id": "c693635b-fb64-48a0-9b4a-83d16f16e374",
      "recording_id": "37b4b58b-4a49-4350-a78b-68763881d8eb",
      "end_time": 300.89,
      "start_time": 275.75,
      "recording_attendee_id": "8ceb7f8c-82e6-4fe3-9727-6265f68974f1",
      "order_number": 19,
      "text": "Yeah. So um that's that's a good question. Um We are an internet listing service and we work with Facebook marketplace. So working with your available units um and with you obviously to to drive leads and pre qualified leads from facebook and things of that nature. Uh So more or less just to learn a little bit more about how you guys are are"
    },
    {
      "id": "c693635b-fb64-48a0-9b4a-83d16f16e374",
      "recording_id": "37b4b58b-4a49-4350-a78b-68763881d8eb",
      "end_time": 321.83,
      "start_time": 300.89,
      "recording_attendee_id": "8ceb7f8c-82e6-4fe3-9727-6265f68974f1",
      "order_number": 20,
      "text": "handling that and what you're currently doing and seeing if we might be able to help out or even cut costs with a lot of a lot of our partners that we bring on. Um We're relatively one of the cheaper aisles are out there, so different, different alternatives to what you're currently working with and if things aren't working to give a boost and and help out."
    },
    {
      "id": "c693635b-fb64-48a0-9b4a-83d16f16e374",
      "recording_id": "37b4b58b-4a49-4350-a78b-68763881d8eb",
      "end_time": 339.3,
      "start_time": 323.96,
      "recording_attendee_id": "4c6e57ef-ad6a-417e-958b-067695f488b2",
      "order_number": 21,
      "text": "Okay, so I actually don't think we would use the services because um I worked through a waiting list for thirty-two of the units. And past that I always get referrals from housing authorities and such. So I"
    },
    {
      "id": "c693635b-fb64-48a0-9b4a-83d16f16e374",
      "recording_id": "37b4b58b-4a49-4350-a78b-68763881d8eb",
      "end_time": 339.65,
      "start_time": 339.22,
      "recording_attendee_id": "8ceb7f8c-82e6-4fe3-9727-6265f68974f1",
      "order_number": 22,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "id": "c693635b-fb64-48a0-9b4a-83d16f16e374",
      "recording_id": "37b4b58b-4a49-4350-a78b-68763881d8eb",
      "end_time": 341.49,
      "start_time": 339.3,
      "recording_attendee_id": "4c6e57ef-ad6a-417e-958b-067695f488b2",
      "order_number": 23,
      "text": "don't have any vacancies."
