      "recording_attendee_id": "8ceb7f8c-82e6-4fe3-9727-6265f68974f1",
      "order_number": 28,
      "text": "No. Okay. Um and what is if you don't mind me asking? I know you said you work off of the waiting list and obviously that's that's great. What is your uh what is like your sixty day out? Look look look like for uh for move out?"
